<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">    &quot;critical&quot;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">: </span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;[CRITICAL] nginx-05: 502 Bad Gateway → 现象:502, 对象:nginx-05, 检查:upstream连通性&quot;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">,</span></span>
